OL,3,C'Clifton Rapist' Ronald Evans will
OL,4,Cstay in prison
OL,6,FConvicted killer and rapist Ronald
OL,7,FEvans will remain behind bars and
OL,8,Fshould not be transferred to an open
OL,9,Fprison, a parole board has ruled.
OL,11,FRonald Evans, 83, has spent more than
OL,12,Fhalf his life incarcerated.
OL,14,FHe was first jailed for raping and
OL,15,Fmurdering 21-year-old Kathleen
OL,16,FHeathcote in Mansfield, in 1963.
OL,18,FIn 1975 he was released and went on to
OL,19,Fcommit seven rapes in Bristol -
OL,20,Fbecoming dubbed 'The Clifton Rapist'.
