OL,3,C'Clifton Rapist' Ronald Evans will
OL,4,Cstay in prison
OL,6,FHe was eventually caught and put back
OL,7,Fbehind bars when police set a
OL,8,Fhoneytrap, using young female officers
OL,9,Facting as decoys to catch him.
OL,11,FIn November 2023 Evans was found
OL,12,Fguilty of sexually assaulting another
OL,13,Fwoman while out on life licence, and
OL,14,Fjailed for a further four years.
OL,16,FHis case was referred to the parole
OL,17,Fboard by the Secretary of State for
OL,18,FJustice to determine whether he could
OL,19,Fbe safely released on parole licence.
