OL,3,C'Clifton Rapist' Ronald Evans will
OL,4,Cstay in prison
OL,6,FA panel of the parole board can only
OL,7,Fdirect re-release if it is satisfied
OL,8,Fthat it was "no longer necessary for
OL,9,Fthe protection of the public that a
OL,10,Fprisoner remains confined in prison".
OL,12,FHowever, due to his recent additional
OL,13,Fcustodial sentenced it was established
OL,14,FMr Evans cannot be re-released until
OL,15,FNovember 2025 at the earliest.
OL,17,FThe panel also considered Mr Evans'
OL,18,Fsuitability for transfer to open
OL,19,Fconditions.
