OL,3,C'Clifton Rapist' Ronald Evans will
OL,4,Cstay in prison
OL,6,FThe Secretary of State will only
OL,7,Faccept a recommendation for transfer
OL,8,Fto open conditions from the parole
OL,9,Fboard "if the prisoner is assessed to
OL,10,Fbe at low risk of absconding".
OL,12,FThe case was considered at an oral
OL,13,Fhearing on 12 December.
OL,15,FThe panel decided it more likely that
OL,16,FMr Evans would reoffend.
